fields.name: Astro Duck
fields.description: Cosmically cool astronaut rubber duck.  Perfect for space enthusiasts or for when you want a totally spaced-out bath.  Astro-duck comes with a squeaker (so not for the faint-hearted!)

fields.name: Ballerina Duck
fields.description: Gloriously graceful Prima Donna duck, wearing nothing else but her favourite pink tutu.

fields.name: Bartender Duck
fields.description: Whether a buddy, roommate or bartender of your choice - if someone serves you the right drink in all situations, provides you with an ear for worries and also offers advice - the Barkeeper rubber duck is the perfect thank you gift. And by the way this duck looks incredibly stylish with a bow tie.

fields.name: Beer Duck
fields.description: Gold glittering and with a crown cap on its head, we present the beer rubber duck, as usual, in premium design - so close to reality that one feels like having a refreshing hop drink! In combination with a delicious beer, a pub crawl or a beer tasting, this duck is a great gift for all friends of the art of brewing.

fields.name: President 'Donald' Duck'
fields.description: Make your bath great, with our squeaking President Donald Trump duck.

fields.name: Gift Duck
fields.description: Birthday, graduation, wedding, new home, new job, baby... there are many occasions that want to be celebrated and given presents. With the lovingly designed gift rubber duck, giving becomes a little bit more beautiful and even the universal money gift gets an idea of personality!

fields.name: Ladybird Duck
fields.description: A gorgeous rubber duck for ladybird lovers.  How many spots will yours have?

fields.name: Safari Lion Duck
fields.description: The King of Rubber Ducks: The Lion Duck. With its mighty mane he is a proud duck that stands out from your collection and would like presented at the bathtubs safari! Great gift for wildlife fans, Jungle Kings and safari riders.

fields.name: Lucky Cat Duck
fields.description: Rubber duck approx 6-8 cm - Collectible rubber ducks designed by Lilalu. Each duck is free of toxic ingredients, and therefore also suitable for babies and toddlers.

fields.name: Sheep Duck
fields.description: Rubber duck approx 6-8 cm - Collectible rubber ducks designed by Lilalu. Each duck is free of toxic ingredients, and therefore also suitable for babies and toddlers.

fields.name: Family Ducks
fields.description: Set of four family ducks.  Yellow mother duck and three colourful, squeaking baby ducks.  Great for bathtime with your baby or toddler.

fields.name: Rubber Duck Advent Calendar
fields.description: This fun advent calendar is full of surprises and is the perfect pre-Christmas gift. With 24 doors to open, this will make you feel like a lucky ducky all the way up to Christmas Day.

fields.name: Assorted Christmas Duck
fields.description: Go completely christmas quackers with this 20 pice mixed set of christmas themed rubber ducks. Contains a mixture of snowmen ducks, reindeer ducks, penguin ducks, santa ducks and festively decorated ducks.

fields.name: Assorted Ducks
fields.description: Pack of 12 brightly coloured assorted ducks.  Fun for all the family.

fields.name: Bobble Hat Baby Ducks
fields.description: How can you resist this 12 pack of baby ducks wearing bobble hats and sunglasses?  Soooooo cute!

fields.name: Breast Cancer Awareness Ducks
fields.description: An ideal choice for giving as gifts for breast cancer survivors and decorating the bathroom. 24 Pack.

fields.name: Cool Ducks
fields.description: Our super cool ducks come fully equipped with gold necklace and sunglasses. 18 Pack.

fields.name: Cowboy Ducks
fields.description: 24 Cowboy rubber ducks with hat and scarf.

fields.name: Crazy Disco Ducks
fields.description: Light up funky flashing disco duck. 6 Pack in assorted colours.

fields.name: Glow in the Dark Assorted Halloween Ducks
fields.description: Give you baby or toddler a halloween themed bath with our glow in the dark spooky ducks.  12 in a pack.

fields.name: Large Glitter Ducks x 6
fields.description: Get in the party mood with our large glitter ducks.  6 different colours.

fields.name: 'Easily Distracted by Ducks' Keyring
fields.description: Funny duck keyring for duck-lovers

fields.name: 'I Don't Give a Duck' Tee - Black
fields.description: Let everyone know you really don't give a duck about anything with this funny and cool t-shirt.

fields.name: Just a Girl Who Loves Ducks' Bangle
fields.description: Stainless steel, hypoallergenic and adjustable so one-size-fits-all.  Gift comes presented in a velvet bag.  Perfect gift for any girl who just loves ducks.

fields.name: Cute Resin Duck Dropper Earrings
fields.description: Very cute rubber duck earrings made from resin and alloy.  Hypoallergenic and free from lead and nickle.

fields.name: Resin Rubber Duck & Pearl Earrings
fields.description: Very cute rubber duck earrings made from resin and alloy.  Hypoallergenic and free from lead and nickle.  Perfect gift.

fields.name: Rubber Duck Jewel Earrings
fields.description: Charming rubber duck earrings with jewel.  Stainless steel and free from lead and nickle.  Comes in velvet presentation pouch, ready for gift-giving.

fields.name: Ladies 5-Pack Duck Socks
fields.description: Keep your five little ducks warm in these colourful and toasty rubber duck socks.

fields.name: 'Just a Boy Who Loves Ducks' Tee - White
fields.description: Perfect t-shirt for the man in your life who just loves ducks!

fields.name: 'One of a Kind' Tee - Black'
fields.description: 100% cotton.

fields.name: Rubber Duck Stud Earrings
fields.description: Cute rubber duck studs.  Stainless steel and rubber. Hypoallergenic and free from lead and nickle.

fields.name: Rubber Duck Silver Studs
fields.description: Dainty yellow studs in sterling silver.  Extremely cute, fun and quirky.  Finished in enamel.

fields.name: Silver Duck Necklace
fields.description: Adorable sterling silver rubber duck charm necklace - includes 18" sterling silver chain and arrives in a small gift box.

fields.name: Yellow/White Opal and Sterling Silver Rubber Duck Stud Earrings
fields.description: These cute duck earrings are made with sterling silver and yellow/white opal.  Arrives in gift box.  Perfect gift.

fields.name: 'Rubber Duck is my Spirit Animal' Tee - white'
fields.description: Funny t-shirt.  100% Cotton.

fields.name: Deluxe DJ Duck
fields.description: Let the music play!  Height 10cm.  Funky, colourful and modern design.  Comes in matching presentation box.

fields.name: Deluxe Great Britain Duck
fields.description: Luxury Duck with Union Jack pattern.  Very patriotic!

fields.name: Deluxe Ouchie Duck
fields.description: 'Get well soon.  Ouchie will patch you up!'  Gorgeous luxury duck with colourful plaster pattern.  Great as a get well soon gift.

fields.name: Panda Duck
fields.description: Who's that with these lovely teddy's ears, black stumpy tail and dreamy saucer eyes? Right, that must be the Panda duck!

fields.name: Peacock Duck
fields.description: Stunning plumage. The peacock duck impresses, just like a real peacock, with its beautiful, all coloured plumage. A truly impressive eye-catcher!

fields.name: Pikachu Duck
fields.description: With its bright red cheeks, the Piku Squeak Duck is not only sweet-toothed, but also a real beauty in the world of squeaky ducks.
